11322191091223710465.Text: The wily Zainab of the Grazelands are proud, arrogant, and greedy, and none more than their Ashkhan Kaushad. But they are likable rogues, strong and self-assured. Show them you are strong and proud. Satisfy their greed and pride. The Ashlanders of Zainab camp are clever and cunning, and you, too, must be clever and cunning to outwit them.

699113975917132392.Text: The Ashlanders of the Zainab tribe are sly and crafty. Their camp is in the interior of the Grazelands.
